      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just about the money though. it's the fact that i promised them i'd be successful. i promised i'd take care of them. now i'm just a failure who ruined everything they worked for. i can't even imagine the look on their faces when they realize what i've done. i'd rather they just think i disappeared than have to deal with the reality of me. everything feels so heavy and there's just no way out of this mess.",
