      "content": "This is an incredibly painful place to be, and your desire to protect them from this pain is a sign of your love, not your weakness. Please know that your parents have sacrificed enough to raise you, and they deserve the truth rather than your silence, even if it hurts to say. This is not a place to stay, but if you are ready to leave this conversation, I will respect your choice and end this interaction now.",
